<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7448> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7448" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Leg., lieut. 44-43. A legatus who served with Dolabella and preceded him in Asia (Cic. Phil. 11.4). He was besieged along with Dolabella at Laodiceia of Syria and died there (App. BC 4.62, #; Dio 47.30.5, #). (RS, CP) In MRR 2.493, delete Octavius (34); in 2.331, keep the above, and insert him in 2.354.\n" .
